commit message:
goods_full tree: Correct an examples count.

This is already correct in (my merge request for) the Web UI here:
https://github.com/murraycu/Galaxy-Zoo/blob/master/app/lib/goods_full_tree.coffee
IconsCacheTest: Check the example icons for checkboxes too.
Add a text file about how to change the surveys used.

IconsCacheTest: Check that the example image is really available.

This fails currently because these fixes have not yet been applied:
https://github.com/zooniverse/Galaxy-Zoo/issues/190

But this test will be useful next time to find similar problems.

ZooniverseClient: Make some some HTTPUrlConnections are disconnect()ed.

These appear to be leaks.

Add some final keywords.

Because I like that.
DecisionTree: Ensure that a field is initialized.

Make some methods static.

Because they can be.
Use constants for simple repeatedly-allocated projection arrays.

SubjectAdder, SyncAdapter: Pass null for instead of an empty array for the sortOrder.

It really doesn't seem to need to be non-null, though I thought so at some time.
